msgid ""
"Item statuses (`lost <#lost>`__, `not for loan <#notforloan>`__, `damaged "
"<#damageauth>`__, `withdrawn <#withdrawnauth>`__)"
msgstr ""
"館藏狀態 (`遺失 <#lost>`__、`不外借 <#notforloan>`__、`毀損 "
