"defaultlongoverduedays-label>` &amp; :ref:`DefaultLongOverdueDays "
"<defaultlongoverduelostvalue-&-defaultlongoverduedays-label>` 偏好。"

#: ../../source/15_implementation_checklist.rst:137
msgid "Localization Configuration"
