msgstr ":ref:`todaysIssuesDefaultSortOrder`：當天借出的館藏顯示於讀者記錄內"

#: ../../source/15_implementation_checklist.rst:202
msgid ""
":ref:`previousIssuesDefaultSortOrder` : Decide how items checked out prior "
