#: ../../source/15_implementation_checklist.rst:275
msgid ""
":ref:`soundon <audioalerts-label>` : Decide if you want to have sounds on "
"for circulation actions"
msgstr ":ref:`開啟音效 <audioalerts-label>`：流通作業時是否發出音效"

